org.apache.plc4x.java.opm

Interface AliasRegistry

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleAliasRegistry

    public interface AliasRegistry
    This interface can be used to give "aliases" for field names in PlcEntitys PlcField strings. These are then resolved.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean canResolve(String alias)
      Checks if this registry can resolve this alias
      boolean canResolve(String connection, String alias)
      Checks if this registry can resolve this alias for the given connection.
      String resolve(String alias)
      Resolves an alias to a valid PLC Field Address
      String resolve(String connection, String alias)
      Resolves an alias to a valid PLC Field based on the connection.

    • Method Detail

      • resolve

        String resolve(String connection,
               String alias)
        Resolves an alias to a valid PLC Field based on the connection. This means that the same alias could be resolved to different Addresses for different connections.
